{"tid":1369294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[路邊社的士佬爆料] 元朗鄉黑收錢打人","createTime":"2019-07-26T16:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T16:14:04.000Z","uid":291104,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f80d8d83bf48a2c4a1a195596d19c0d7e3c85631","tid":1369294,"uid":291104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:11:46.000Z","msg":"Sorry我係P牌絲打，第一次連登發ＰＯＳＴ，<br />\n我係長期做ＣＤ－ＣＯＭ，但因為今日發夢搭的士，夢中遇著一個怒火的士佬，爆左勁多野俾我聽，我無從FACT CHECK，但都仍然特登整個account，好想上黎講幾句報兩單料。唔岩聽的遇左大家腐皮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說車上收音機播新聞講到元朗恐襲，然後的士佬話佢琴日岩岩車正個黑社會，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑社會同佢講，元朗單野，原來本身吹雞講好左係人人派$5000，<br />\n點知完事後，每人只係得$2000，班黑道梗係媽媽聲，據說仲郁到６個大佬，有３個走得甩。<br />\n（其實我就腦補左何妖單野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n仲有，佢仲爆左，<br />\nＤ白衫入面，其　實　係　有　警　犬　的。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但其實佢成程車一開車佢就講，越講越激動。因為佢係白粉報mode（又鬧示威者又鬧政府），我一路聽一路９hea佢一路心勁驚佢炒車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後佢就話自己係住深圳乜乜７７，話其實大陸早就安排左６萬解放軍駐左喺深圳Stand By，又話又去左湛江訓練，車出車入深圳好多Ｄ人都睇到，等班暴徒攪丫，乜乜７７<br />\n我冒著生命危險講左句，<br />\n係出解放軍就快ｄ，我等緊攬炒，睇下有錢佬多樓ｄ定我多樓ｄ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一句收左佢皮，即刻靜哂<br />\n<br />\nDead Air左一陣好在就到左，個夢就發完，好在冇炒車。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa6131b07cc2e3082f967fd370d2e1fe62b8d2d","tid":1369294,"uid":69159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T16:14:04.000Z","msg":"十級警報！！分化撚割蓆撚出現係連登<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1369161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1369161</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n故事80分 幾精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}